{"type": "article", "id": 25510, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-15T10:27:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2591, "name": "地震"}, {"id": 26123, "name": "抗议活动"}, {"id": 2105, "name": "科比"}, {"id": 12666, "name": "费德勒"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607164208m7WNbxH50iLhJ6O3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、日本熊本发生地震</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164156HOdVYNW69sozZEbl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当地时间 4 月 14 日晚，日本熊本县发生了 6.4 级强震，目前已经造成 9 人死亡，650 人重伤。著名景点熊本城天守阁在地震中遭到损毁。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164157XFt6kafsJEyec35I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">JIJI PRESS/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">工作人员在熊本城勘查受灾情况。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164158UNve2DKf1Hs8qVnA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">灾民裹着毯子坐在街头避难。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164158GneyXtOVkPjBM4LN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">强震引发九州自动车道路面坍塌。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、科比告别战</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164159Ht1U9x47yeFP6KTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164159wA9GfQmvl5SytCj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FREDERIC J. BROWN/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164200YrnfxHOcz4QiNdZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Harry How/GettyNorthAmerica/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071642008ToQYzxmUdvGRjlL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Andrew D. Bernstein/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>15/16 NBA 常规赛，湖人 101-96 爵士，科比砍下 60 分完美谢幕。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、西班牙学生罢课</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164201EpRi2P5BnWI1hJ9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">西班牙马德里，学生举行 48 小时罢课活动，抗议削减教育经费和体制改革。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、暗黑“麦当劳叔叔”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164203WgLyME7bk8FD95zr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Cris Faga/CON/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">巴西圣保罗（Sao Paulo），抗议者装扮成“麦当劳叔叔”，为麦当劳员工争取权利。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、ATP 蒙特卡洛大师赛</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164203x85DkifBR9cGUd10.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">VALERY HACHE/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">摩纳哥，2016 ATP 蒙特卡洛大师赛男单第 3 轮，费德勒 2-0 阿古特。<br></p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、西沙群岛</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071642043J78u45ftHvMj2Zy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">西沙群岛的海军守备部队。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、纪念莎翁</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071642063TQtA5i9gpyZn6sC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">英国伦敦，“Shakespeare in Ten Acts”展举行了媒体预展，一位参观者拉开印有人物的门帘。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、尼泊尔“朱砂大战”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164207XDzKATFikcVdhNLf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">尼泊尔巴克塔普尔（Bhaktapur），民众上演“朱砂大战”，庆祝 Sindoor Jatra 节。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、1600 只纸大熊猫亮相巴黎</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164207PInNTRYyc0bFm1e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">法国巴黎，1600 只纸大熊猫亮相一处商场。该活动于 2008 年由世界野生动物基金会（WWF）发起，提醒人们世界上现存的大熊猫数量，呼吁人们保护濒危动物。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、油菜花田</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164208B3ITcFH9p4qdbAoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">法国多尔多涅（Dordogne）的一处油菜花田。</p>\n\n\n"}